short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Shows data on the current mayor, recent news, and other miscellaneous information from Hypixel Skyblock.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension shows data on the current mayor in Hypixel Skyblock and the current elections, if applicable, using Hypixel API.
